About:
------
pulsar is a libevent based multi-threaded web server

Build:
------
git clone git://github.com/abhinavsingh/pulsar.git
cd pulsar/
make
./pulsar

Help:
-----
Usage: ./pulsar [-p port] [-w workers] [-h]

Options:
  -p port        : tcp port number to listen on (default: 9090)
  -w workers     : number of worker threads to start for accepting connections (default: 4)
  -h             : display this help message